videos.description: Urban Meyer on Ohio State's preparation for the Playstation Fiesta Bowl
videos.headline: Urban Meyer on Ohio State's preparation for the Playstation Fiesta Bowl

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney confident in team's leadership
videos.headline: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney confident in team's leadership

videos.description: Clemson's Deshaun Watson throws an interception to Ohio State's Gareon Conley on the opening drive.
videos.headline: Watson's first pass of the game picked off

videos.description: Deshaun Watson finds Mike Williams who goes 37 yards for the Clemson first down.
videos.headline: Watson finds Williams on the slant for a 37-yard gain

videos.description: Tyler Durbin misses his second field goal attempt of the game for Ohio State.
videos.headline: Ohio State misses its second FG of the game

videos.description: Deshaun Watson takes it himself for a one-yard touchdown to put Clemson up 10-0.
videos.headline: Watson runs it in for the 1st TD of the game

videos.description: Deshaun Watson throws his second interception of the game, this one to Ohio State's Malik Hooker, his seventh of the season.
videos.headline: Watson throws his second INT

videos.description: Deshaun Watson connects with C.J. Fuller for a 30-yard touchdown to put the Tigers up 17-0.
videos.headline: Watson lobs it to Fuller for a 30-yard TD

videos.description: Despite a pair of Deshaun Watson interceptions, Clemson has found the end zone twice to take a 17-0 lead over Ohio State into halftime.
videos.headline: Clemson rolling in the first half over Ohio State

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Sweeney reflects on both the positive and negative play from Clemson's 1st half performance.
videos.headline: Dabo Sweeney talks about the challenges that Clemson faced in the 1st half

videos.description: Urban Meyer talks about Ohio State's performance in the 1st half and how they improve in the 2nd half
videos.headline: Urban Meyer discusses mistakes made in the 1st half

videos.description: Mike Weber fumbles for Ohio State on their first drive of the 2nd half and Clemson recovers.
videos.headline: Buckeyes fumble on their first drive of the second half

videos.description: Greg Huegel misses a 31-yard field goal where two Ohio State defenders jump offside but get back before the snap.
videos.headline: Clemson misses field goal after no offside call

videos.description: Deshaun Watson rushes seven yards for his second touchdown of the game, giving Clemson a 24-0 lead over Ohio State.
videos.headline: Watson scores on the ground for a second time

videos.description: J.T. Barrett's pass is intercepted by Cordrea Tankersley who returns it 18 yards before being pushed out.
videos.headline: Tipped pass leads to interception for Clemson

videos.description: J.T. Barrett throws an interception on 4th and long, as Clemson's Van Smith returns it 86 yards.
videos.headline: Barrett picked off in the endzone

videos.description: Wayne Gallman runs the sweep into the endzone to put Clemson up 31-0.
videos.headline: Gallman takes it to the corner for the TD in Clemson win

videos.description: The Clemson Tigers left no doubt to whether they deserve another shot at Alabama, thanks to a 31-0 victory over Ohio State in the PlayStation Fiesta Bowl.
videos.headline: Clemson cruises past Ohio State towards Alabama rematch

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Sweeney credits this win as a team effort and talks about his feelings towards playing Alabama in a rematch of last year's CFP National Championship game.
videos.headline: Sweeney on shutout of OSU, advancing for rematch with Alabama

videos.description: Clemson quarterback Deshaun Watson discusses his performance in the Fiesta Bowl.
videos.headline: Deshaun Watson talks about winning the Fiesta Bowl

videos.description: Awarding the Clemson Tigers the Playstation Fiesta Bowl trophy, along with Offensive and Defensive players of the game honors.
videos.headline: Trophy Presentation for Clemson's 31-0 victory over Ohio State in the Playstation Fiesta Bowl

videos.description: Urban Meyer thought his defense played well, but with a lack of any kind of offense, Clemson was too much for Ohio State to handle in a 31-0 loss.
videos.headline: Meyer disappointed in offensive performance

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Urban Meyer disappointed with offensive performance) 2016/12/31

videos.description: Rece Davis joins Scott Van Pelt and discusses the importance of Clemson defeating Ohio State in order to once again challenge Alabama for the national title.
videos.headline: A victory over Ohio State needed to happen for Clemson

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (A victory over Ohio State needed to happen for Clemson) 2016/12/31 SVP SC

videos.description: Deshaun Watson throws for 259 yards and a touchdown, adding 57 yards and two scores on the ground, as Clemson blanks Ohio State 31-0 for a rematch with Alabama.
videos.headline: Watson, Clemson rout Ohio State to advance to CFP championship
